h4. Actor:
Administrator.

h4. Description:
Name of use case represents its functionality.

h4. Flow:
* Actor clicks [Exchange House|guide:_ShowExchangeHousePlugin] option from top menu bar.
* Click *Agent* sub menu from left menu.
* Click *Agent* link.
* [Show Landing Page of *Agent*|guide:ShowExhAgentActionService].
* Select a Line-Item from grid view.
* Click "User" button from tool bar.
* [Show Landing Page of "User-Agent Mapping"|guide:ShowUserAgentActionService].
* Click the magnify icon from grid view.
* Write searching criteria.
* Press "Enter" button.
* Search "User-Agent Mapping" From Grid View.

h4. Pre-condition:
* User must have "List User Agent" privilege.
* Rules of Searching:
{table}
*Field* | *Input Type* | *Data Type* | *Searching Option*	
Find | Text Box | Alpha Numeric | User Name
Find | Text Box | Alpha Numeric | Agent Name
{table}


h4. Process:
* Get list of "User-Agent Mapping" (default: 15 at Max) matching with search criteria.
* Searching with zero length string will show list of all "User-Agent Mapping".

h4. Post-condition:

* *Success:*
** "User-Agent Mapping" will be listed in grid view.

* *Failure:*
** Show error message for details visit [Error Handler|common Usecases].

